research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for El Cenizo, TX, were identified from multiple sources, including news articles from November 2022 and official directories. Carina Hernandez was elected Mayor, and Juany Valdez (also referred to as San Juanita Valdez) and Daisy Perez were elected as City Commissioners. El Cenizo operates as a Type C General Law City with a Mayor and two City Commissioners elected at large.
